    units unless otherwise agreed upon by the two parties.

  p.md-title[style='padding-bottom: 10px;'] Payment Terms
  p.md-subhead[style='padding-bottom: 10px; font-style: italic;'] What are our
    payment terms?
  p.md-subhead The Customer shall pay the Company
  p.md-subhead Buyer will pay Seller within 30 days of the date of Seller’s
    invoice, and a 1% discount will be applied to payments received within 10
    days of the invoice date, provided there is no use of credits and payments
    are made in immediately good funds by check, wire, or ACH.  
  p.md-subhead[style='padding-bottom: 30px;'] If Buyer’s account goes 30 days or
    more past due, Buyer irrevocably authorizes Seller to charge the past due
    amount to the credit card on file.

  p.md-title[style='padding-bottom: 10px;'] Tolerance for Overage and Shortage
  p.md-subhead[style='padding-bottom: 30px;'] The Customer understands that
    there is a maximum of a % tolerance for an overage or shortage in
    production for custom orders. In the case that there is an overage or
    shortage in production, the Company will inform the Customer of the specific
    styles or items that have been overproduced or underproduced. The Customer
    agrees to accept any additional items and pay the adjusted balance, whether
    higher or lower.

  p.md-title[style='padding-bottom: 10px;'] Notice of Defects/Returns
  p.md-subhead The Customer must notify the Company of all claims for damages
    resulting from late delivery or any other defects that are known to the
    Customer at the time the Customer receives the products. Any such claims
    must be made in writing via email to <a href="mailto:sales@richhoney.us"> sales@richhoney.us </a>
    Any other correspondence not made via e-mail shall be considered null.
  p.md-subhead[style='padding-bottom: 30px;'] Any claims of defects, including
    but not limited to those related to quality or identity must be made within
    7 days of receipt of the products. The Customer agrees that 7 days is a
    reasonable period of time to make such claims and agrees to inspect all
