  p.md-title[style='padding-bottom: 10px;'] Returns
  p.md-subhead[style='font-style: italic;']Do we have a return policy?
  p.md-subhead[style='padding-bottom: 30px;'] Except as otherwise stated herein,
    merchandise may be returned within 7 days of receipt of the merchandise, and
    are subject to a 20% restocking fee, with a $5.00 minimum charge. A written
    authorization from Company must be obtained by Customer for any returned
